8200.name: Fisherman's Potion - White
8200.description: By lowering one's fishing skill level, this potion allows one to catch a white fish (level 22~24 fish). If one uses a potion that is designed for a higher fishing skill level than one's own, the potion will have no effect. Fisherman's Potion Green

8201.name: Fisherman's Potion - Black
8201.description: By lowering one's fishing skill level, this potion allows one to catch a green fish (level 25~27 fish). If one uses a potion that is designed for a higher fishing skill level than one's own, the potion will have no effect.

8202.name: Fisherman's Potion
8202.description: Restores a player's fishing mastery level, which was lowered by the Fisherman's Potion, back to the previous level. Fisherman's Recovery Potion
